Uses of Interface
xxl.core.collections.containers.recordManager.TIdManager

  • Packages that use TIdManager 
    Package Description
    xxl.core.collections.containers.recordManager
    Provides a decorator container that is able to store records (of type Block ) which are of different size.

    • Uses of TIdManager in xxl.core.collections.containers.recordManager

      Classes in xxl.core.collections.containers.recordManager that implement TIdManager 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  IdentityTIdManager
      This class implements the TIdManager interface and always returns the same Object (identity).
      class  MapTIdManager
      This class implements a TIdManager which uses a main memory HashMap to store the relationship between external identifyers (of type Long) and tuple identifyers inside the record manager.
      Methods in xxl.core.collections.containers.recordManager that return TIdManager 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      TIdManager RecordManager.getTIdManager()
      Returns the tupel identifyer manager which is used.
      static TIdManager Utility.getTIdManager(int tidManagerNumber, FixedSizeConverter converter)
      Returns a new TIdManager with the given number and converter.
